entry.title: Grabcartoons v2.7
entry.content: Last night I made a new release of my comic aggregator script, <a href="http://zzamboni.org/grabcartoons/">grabcartoons</a>. You can fetch it from it brand new <a href="http://zzamboni.org/grabcartoons/">web page</a>, now hosted by <a href="http://github.com/zzamboni/grabcartoons/">github.com</a> instead of sourceforge.net.
